# wetlab/data/ — read-out data from CRO pilots (sensitive)
#
# Default: NOTHING in this directory is committed to git.
# Anonymized read-outs are intended to live here locally for analysis,
# but the raw data may contain PHI / proprietary CRO data / IP-sensitive
# sequences and is NOT to be pushed to a public repo.
#
# If you need to commit summary data (e.g., aggregated kinetics curves
# for a paper), explicitly add: git add -f wetlab/data/<summary-file>
# after legal review.

# Ignore everything
*
# Except this file itself
!.gitignore
!README.md
